===Intransitive verb===
'''to lock''' ([[locks]], [[locked]], [[locking]])

# To become fastened in place
#: ''If you put the brakes on too hard, the wheels will lock.''
#''([[break dancing]])'' To freeze ones body or a part thereof in place
#: ''a pop and lock routine''

